No. 689. No. 690. Catharine J. White, Executrix, etc., Petitioner, v. The Pennsylvania Railroad Company; and Catharine J. White, Executrix, etc., Petitioner, v. The Steam Ferry Boat Philadelphia, etc. April 15, 1907. Mr. James J. Macklin and Mr. LaRoy 8. Gove for petitioner. Mr. Henry Galbraith Ward for respondents.

Petitions for writs of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
